ho seek my life will be destroyed; they will go down to the depths of the earth.<br>但那些寻索要灭我命的人，必往地底下去。<br><br><br>诗63:10 <br>They will be given over to the sword and become food for <x-word word="jackals"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #800000;">jackals</span></x-word>.<br>他们必被刀剑所杀，被野狗所吃。<br><br><br>诗63:11 <br>But the king will <x-group group="rejoiceXin"><span style="box-shadow: 0px 3px white, 0px 4px #00BFFF;"><x-word word="rejoice"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">rejoice</span></x-word> in</span></x-group> God; all who swear by God's name will praise him, while the mouths of <x-word word="liars"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">liars</span></x-word> will be silenced.<br>但是王必因 神欢喜，凡指着他发誓的，必要夸口，因为说谎之人的口必被塞住。</p>

